an uncomfortable ride home.

01:15.632 --> 01:16.931
Tough crowd.

01:16.933 --> 01:18.433
Who picked this book?

01:18.435 --> 01:20.135
Yeah, but the moral was so sweet.

01:20.137 --> 01:22.203
If you truly love something,
it'll never go away.

01:22.205 --> 01:24.239
Oh, that's ludicrous.

01:24.241 --> 01:26.374
I love this library, and
they're taking it away.

01:26.376 --> 01:27.842
